channel.title: Help me please
channel.description:
Okay I'm running a Mac OS X Version 10.5.8 and I'm having some issues. I can't find a server that is compatible with my mac.
Can someone give me a client/Webclient that will work for me? I'm not very good with computer stuff i just like to play. If someone could help me I'd much appreciate it.
Even if someone could give me a tutorial on how to make one work, that would be excellent.
Cheers.
